From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tsf-sync contributors <tsf-sync@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] wifi: ath11k: add KUnit tests for PTP hardware clock

KUnit tests for the ath11k PTP hardware clock.

Test suites:

  ath11k_ptp_find_vdev:
    - empty list, one started, one stopped, first-match (4 cases)

  ath11k_ptp_adjtime_sign:
    - documents (u32)delta_us cast behavior (5 parameterized)
    - negative deltas wrap to large positive (firmware limitation)

  ath11k_ptp_contract:
    - gettime64/settime64 return -EOPNOTSUPP
    - adjfine returns 0

Total: 12 tests.

Signed-off-by: tsf-sync contributors <tsf-sync@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 3 files changed, 289 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/Kconfig b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/Kconfig
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/Kconfig	2026-04-05 09:06:19.203689737 -0700
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/Kconfig	2026-04-05 09:06:19.222723844 -0700
@@ -12,6 +12,19 @@
 
 	  If you choose to build a module, it'll be called ath11k.
 
